<br>
So, where is it that we finally catch up to do even a reasonable level of damage on mobs?  44 or so?<br>
<br>
<br>
Why don't you leave your filters off, and join a group in the level 20 to 25 range, watch the melees do so much damage, and then you will have your answer.  The 30 to 43 range, known for being difficult, well, has THAT been improved?<br>
<br>
You say you havn't seen it, but try grouping, and see for yourself. <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
